l3afpad: l3afpad (a notepad clone for GTK3)
l3afpad:
l3afpad: l3afpad is a simple GTK3 text editor that emphasizes simplicity.
l3afpad: As development focuses on keeping weight down to a minimum,
l3afpad: only the most essential features are implemented in the editor.
l3afpad: l3afpad is simple to use, it's easily compiled, requires few
l3afpad: libraries, and starts up quickly.
l3afpad:
l3afpad: https://github.com/stevenhoneyman/l3afpad
